headline: XPO Stock Sees Relative Strength Rating Jump To 80
summary: On Friday, XPO stock received a positive adjustment to its Relative Strength (RS) Rating, from 69 to 80. This exclusive rating from Investor's Business Daily identifies price action with a 1 (worst) to 99 (best) score.
